          <head type="note" n="1" xml:id="spp-334-24JK-headnote-1">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-334-24JK-headnote-1-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-334-24JK-headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1"><hi rend="italics">The Number printed of the </hi>Journal<hi rend="italics"> in which the following Poems were inserted, not being near sufficient to answer the Demand made for them, it has been thought proper to reprint them in this; to make room for which, we have been oblig'd to omit some Advertisements which were sent for this Paper</hi>.</l>
            </lg>
